                Grammar products and higher-dimensional grammars
description:
                This library provides the framework for the automatic
                generation of complex grammars from more simple building
                blocks. Internally, grammars are written using ADPfusion
                operations and yield efficient code.
                .
                We provide a library with a parser for grammatical constructs.
                Parsed grammars can be combined in several ways and transformed
                into ADPfusion constructs which yield efficient implementations
                of the combined grammars. Alternatively, such combined grammars
                may be pretty-printed using the "GrammarProducts" executable.
